SELECT * FROM "atoms" WHERE "entity_id" = '599c96938d1fe084243282' and "product_id" = '5' ORDER BY "id" DESC LIMIT 1

SELECT "comments".* FROM "comments" inner join "atoms" on "comments"."atom_entity_id" = "atoms"."entity_id" WHERE "atom_entity_id" = '599c96938d1fe084243282' and "product_id" = '5' and "comments"."deleted_at" IS NULL GROUP BY "comments"."id" ORDER BY "comments"."id" ASC
